query:
SELECT id, email, name, accountStatus, createdAt
FROM users
WHERE email IN (
  SELECT email 
  FROM users 
  WHERE email IS NOT NULL
  GROUP BY email 
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
)
ORDER BY email, createdAt;
